  "steps": [
    "Add 1.5 g LB powder, 1.5 g agarose powder to conical flask",
    "Dilute with 200 mL distilled water. Ensure fully dissolved",
    "Seal conical flask with sponge bung and foil",
    "Sterilise growth medium by autoclaving"
